    <refname>&dhpackage;</refname>

    <refpurpose>Renames files based on their title.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <cmdsynopsis>
      <command>&dhpackage;</command>
         <arg><replaceable>files</replaceable></arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsect1>
    <title>DESCRIPTION</title>

    <para>This manual page documents briefly the
      <command>&dhpackage;</command> command.</para>

    <para><command>&dhpackage;</command> renames all the files
    on the command-line based on their IMDB titles. Files have all 
    extensions copied and appended to the title of the film to create
    the new filename.
    </para>


  </refsect1>
